headline: US Financial 15 Split Corp. Preferred Dividend Declared

Distributions are payable February 10, 2026 to shareholders on record as at January 30, 2026. headline: Fifth Third Bancorp’s (NASDAQ:FITB) Q4 CY2025 Earnings Results: Revenue In Line With Expectations
summary: Regional banking company Fifth Third Bancorp (NASDAQ:FITB) met Wall Streets revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales up 4.9% year on year to $2.34 billion. Its GAAP profit of $1.04 per share was 4.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
